<HEAD>Computers Abort Shuttle Test Firing in Final Moments</HEAD>
<HEAD>LaserPhotos CSB2, CSB5</HEAD>
<NOTE>Eds: LEADS with 10 grafs to update with possibility long exposure
to cold fuel might have affected sensor. Pick up 7th graf pvs, `The
